data.description: HOME WARRANTY!! Exceptional 4BR/2.5BA Home with a Pool and Loft! Needs some TLC and is priced accordingly. The spacious kitchen features abundant cabinetry, a convenient pantry, a central island, and a cozy breakfast area. The main bedroom suite is a true retreat, complete with a private balcony, vaulted ceilings, a separate soaking tub and shower, dual sinks, and a generous walk-in closet. The backyard is your personal oasis, ideal for both entertaining and relaxation. It boasts a sparkling fenced pool, a covered patio, and extended pavers for outdoor enjoyment. This gem of a home has great potential, and once you see it, you'll want to make it your own!
